               <p>JOHN LEE. I am servant to Mr. Sawyer; the prisoner was a lodger in his house, and this sheet was on a bed in the room where the prisoner lay; but not on the bed he slept in. I missed the sheet on the 7th in the morning. An officer came in and asked if we had lost a sheet; we told him we had. It was marked all over, "Sawyer, <placeName id="t18160918-171-crimeloc892">Wingfield-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18160918-171-crimeloc892" type="placeName" value="Wingfield-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18160918-171-crimeloc892" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160918-171-off890 t18160918-171-crimeloc892"></join>, stop the bearer."</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160918-171-person1182">
                  THOMAS 
                  JONES
               <interp inst="t18160918-171-person1182" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
