                     <interp inst="t18160918-171-person1182" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner wanted to sell this sheet to me; but I knew it must have been stolen by the stamp, and I gave him in charge of an officer.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. In distress</p>
